              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_clinical_intervention">CLINICAL INTERVENTION</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_chemoradiotherapy">Chemoradiotherapy</xref>
 (also known as 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_chemoradiotherapy">Chemoradiation</xref>) is a treatment that combines 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_chemotherapy">Chemotherapy</xref>
 with radiation therapy.        </p>
